&lt;p&gt;This is a unique opportunity to join an early-stage company led by serial entrepreneur &lt;strong&gt;Andrew Filev&lt;/strong&gt; (founder of a unicorn startup), and shape a product that is redefining how software is built.&lt;/p&gt;
